description: Normalized log2ratio protein abundance estimates for the CPTAC Uterine Corpus Endometrial Carcinoma (UCEC) Proteome study (PDC Study ID: PDC000125) were obtained via the PDC API quantDataMatrix endpoint.  These data are part of the CPTAC3 Discovery project.  More information on the pipeline and the results generated by it can be found here: https://pdc.cancer.gov/data-dictionary/harmonization.html
friendlyName: CPTAC3-DISCOVERY UTERINE CORPUS ENDOMETRIAL CARCINOMA (UCEC) PROTEOME
